Package com.audiophile.t2m.text

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DatabaseHandler  
    DatabaseHandler.Entry
    Represents an entry in the database
    Sentence
    A class that represents a sentence in a text and holds it meta data and analytics values.
    TextAnalyser
    A group of functions that break a text apart and analyse it.
    Word
    Represents a word in the text and holds its name, tendency and effect from the database.
    WordFilter
    This class filters all filler words from a text.
